/Error explation, so error name: Navigator operation requested with a context that does not include a Navigator in Flutter.
/If you want to solve this problem, please see this steps. We have to do 2 steps. These are:
 -----------------------------------------  -----------------------------------------  ----------------------------------------- 
                                              /Changing the runApp code like this: 
-This Old code from top: 
void main() {                                      
runApp(const MyApp());            
}

 -----------------------------------------  -----------------------------------------  ----------------------------------------- 
-This is new code from top:
void main() {
  runApp(MaterialApp(
      home: MyApp()));
  }                                           #So,  we changed the top code which started with RunApp...
   ----------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------  ----------------------------------------- 
                                              /Changing the Stless/Stful code like this:
  
  /This is old code from widget class:
   return MaterialApp(
      home: Scaffold(),
      );                                      
 ----------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------  ----------------------------------------- 
  /This is new code from widget class:
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Scaffold();                        #So,  we changed the class code which started with return MaterialApp...
 ----------------------------------------- -----------------------------------------  ----------------------------------------- 
Also, if you don't understand the article, you can watch the video to solve the problem for understanding more truely.
The video: https://bit.ly/3cqARhf
  
  
